{"tid":195254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[尊貴的士狗] 亂晒龍！小巴打蛇餅 call的都冇用「去屯門都唔接」","createTime":"2017-04-10T13:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T00:20:25.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"136cabc16fee450a844ef8137f231b5e71e4024c","tid":195254,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"港鐵繁忙時間又發生故障，觀塘綫九龍灣站的架空電纜出現故障，觀塘站至九龍塘站列車服務仍暫停。大批乘客離開港鐵站，令觀塘道以至整個觀塘區一帶行人路擠得水洩不通，部分人索性行路出彩虹道至龍翔道，再覓其他方法回家。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘區一帶小巴站大排長龍，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>的士更是「一架難求」，即使一些「八折黨」的士也稱該區一帶「亂晒龍」，司機根本入不到該處，又或是恐怕「有入冇出」，「觀塘去屯門order都唔接呀」</strong></span>。<br />\n港鐵表示，觀塘綫事故已於晚上8時25分完成處理，列車服務陸續回復正常。"},{"pid":"d8ca8782cbf2b9f2a27da5a9817dea3f25a589d9","tid":195254,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"拒載 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec5222e4f4132dc698067f50223244d83b11a28","tid":195254,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4152b9a3f9ba5a4247c41ab91246e8f8f3cdf153","tid":195254,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔係出面行下街 食個飯先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早D返去訓。聽朝要返工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18710dcaa2577958ddea11fae798c1b63fbc9a6","tid":195254,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔係出面行下街 食個飯先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早D返去訓。聽朝要返工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返到去咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前試過又係廢鐵收皮即刻訂張戲飛睇戲食埋飯先慢慢返屋企<i